---
// src/pages/agent-setup.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="AI Agent Setup" description="ZeroDumb's guide to building useful, not-useless AI tools.">
  <div class="terminal-container rounded-lg border border-gray-700 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="terminal-header bg-gray-800 px-4 py-2 flex justify-between items-center">
      <span class="text-gray-300 font-mono">zerodumb@ethics-journal:~/agent-setup$</span>
      <div class="flex space-x-2">
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
        <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none p-6">
      <h1 class="text-terminal-green"> AI Agent Setup</h1>
      <p>
        Building an AI agent? Awesome. Planning to duct tape five APIs, three notebooks, and some whisper of a Python script into production? Less awesome.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-terminal-cyan"> What I'll Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Help you decide whether you need an agent or just a better automation script</li>
        <li>Guide you through choosing the right model, tools, and context window strategy</li>
        <li>Help you avoid turning your agent into an infinite loop of hallucinations</li>
        <li>Set up local or cloud deployment (LangChain, GPT APIs, private models, etc.)</li>
        <li>Offer a review session to make sure it doesn't respond with "I'm sorry Dave..."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-terminal-cyan"> Cost</h2>
      <p><strong>$150+</strong> — Includes setup consultation and follow-up tuning. (No crypto-trading bots allowed. Probably.)</p>
      <p>
        If you're a student or a non-profit, I might be able to help you out for free. Just ask nicely.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-terminal-cyan"> Interested?</h2>
      <a href="mailto:zero@zerodumb.dev" class="inline-block mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-500 text-white rounded">
        Get in Touch
      </a>
      <p>Or, just yell loudly in the comments of a Hacker News thread and maybe I'll hear it.</p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-gray-500">
        ☕ Found this helpful? <a href="https://buymeacoffee.com/iamnotaskid" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline">Buy Me Caffeine &#8599;</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
